==Installation== <!--T:5-->

<!--T:6-->
# Install the FreeGrid Workbench via the [[Image:AddonManager.svg|24px]] [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]]. For manual installation, see [[Installing_more_workbenches|Installing more workbenches]].
# Restart FreeCAD.


